---
By: Lucretius
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 165
    Verse: 9
Tags:
  - Fear is an emotion
---
As children tremble and fear everything in the blind darkness, so we in the
light sometimes fear what is no more to be feared than the things children
in the dark hold in terror and imagine will come true.
